data.description: Price reduced and sellers are motivated! Welcome to this stunning one-story home situated on a desirable corner lot in the heart of Pflugerville, Texas. This home has an assumable VA loan at a fantastic rate of 2.375% and a fantastic price per sq foot for this neighborhood! Boasting a thoughtfully designed floor plan, this residence offers an incredible bonus room upstairs with a full bath and closet, providing endless possibilities for use as a fifth bedroom, guest suite, home office, or recreational space.  Built in 2017, this home showcases modern architecture and a charming curb appeal that is sure to captivate. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting atmosphere filled with natural light and a seamless flow throughout. The main level features a spacious living area, perfect for both relaxation and entertaining, with easy access to the added back patio and a screened-in porch.  Indulge in the pleasures of outdoor living as you step into the backyard oasis, which boasts a lush and meticulously maintained yard adorned with a variety of fruit trees and vibrant rosebushes. Imagine spending tranquil evenings on the patio, savoring the fragrance of blooming flowers and enjoying the privacy offered by the corner lot.  Convenience is at your fingertips with this home's ideal location. Situated in a highly desirable area, you'll find yourself just moments away from shopping centers, supermarkets, and a range of dining options. Families will appreciate the proximity to well-regarded schools, providing an excellent education for children of all ages.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable Pflugerville residence your own. With its spacious layout, versatile bonus room, and enchanting outdoor living space, this home truly offers the best of both comfort and style. Schedule a viewing today and experience the unparalleled lifestyle this property has to offer.
